  "local_port": 36438,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best Indian gaming companies that builds small open world, first-person shooter, 3d games for Ios that you can hire so they can make games for you?",
  "response": "If you're looking to hire Indian game development companies that specialize in creating small open-world, first-person shooter (FPS), and 3D games for iOS, here are some of the best studios known for their expertise in mobile game development:\n\n---\n\n### **1. ** **Zatun**\n   - **Specialization**: Zatun is known for developing high-quality 3D games, including FPS titles like *Suppressed*. They have experience in creating immersive open-world and action-packed games for mobile platforms.\n   - **Website**: [zatun.com](https://www.zatun.com)\n\n---\n\n### **2. ** **Hyperlink InfoSystem**\n   - **Specialization**: A leading game development company in India, Hyperlink InfoSystem has expertise in creating 3D games, including open-world and FPS titles. They have a strong portfolio in mobile game development.\n   - **Website**: [hyperlinkinfosystem.com](https://www.hyperlinkinfosystem.com)\n\n---\n\n### **3. ** **Juego Studios**\n   - **Specialization**: Juego Studios is a well-known Indian game development company with experience in creating 3D games, including open-world and FPS genres. They cater to iOS and Android platforms.\n   - **Website**: [juegostudio.com](https://www.juegostudio.com)\n\n---\n\n### **4. ** **Mobisoft Infotech**\n   - **Specialization**: Mobisoft Infotech develops high-quality 3D mobile games and has experience in creating immersive open-world and FPS games. They have worked on iOS and Android platforms.\n   - **Website**: [mobisoftinfotech.com](https://www.mobisoftinfotech.com)\n\n---\n\n### **5. ** **GameEon Studios**\n   - **Specialization**: GameEon Studios is known for developing 3D racing and action games. While they focus on racing, they have the capability to create open-world and FPS games for iOS.\n   - **Website**: [gameeon.net](https://www.gameeon.net)\n\n---\n\n### **6. ** **Techugo**\n   - **Specialization**: Techugo is a mobile app and game development company with expertise in creating 3D games for iOS. They can handle open-world and FPS game development.\n   - **Website**: [techugo.com](https://www.techugo.com)\n\n---\n\n### **7. ** **Infinity Game Studio**\n   - **Specialization**: Infinity Game Studio focuses on mobile game development, including 3D, open-world, and FPS games. They have experience in developing games for iOS.\n   - **Website**: [infinitygamestudio.com](https://www.infinitygamestudio.com)\n\n---\n\n### **8. ** **HData Systems**\n   - **Specialization**: HData Systems develops 3D games for mobile platforms, including iOS. They have experience in creating engaging open-world and FPS games.\n   - **Website**: [hdatasystems.com](https://www.hdatasystems.com)\n\n---\n\n### **9. ** **OrangeGames**\n   - **Specialization**: OrangeGames is an Indian game development company with expertise in creating 3D mobile games. They can develop open-world and FPS games tailored for iOS.\n   - **Website**: [orangegames.in](https://www.orangegames.in)\n\n---\n\n### **10. ** **AppX**\n   - **Specialization**: AppX is a mobile game development company with experience in creating 3D games for iOS. They can develop open-world and FPS games.\n   - **Website**: [appx.co.in](https://www.appx.co.in)\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Hiring:**\n- **Portfolio Review**: Always check their portfolio for games similar to your vision.\n- **Client Reviews**: Look for testimonials or reviews from past clients.\n- **Technical Expertise**: Ensure they have experience with Unity or Unreal Engine, as these are commonly used for 3D and FPS games.\n- **Communication**: Choose a company that offers clear and timely communication.\n\nThese companies have a proven track record in mobile game development and can help bring your small open-world FPS game idea to life on iOS.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
